{"tid":1721002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[CCTV]荃灣嘉理墮樓案示意圖","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:28:10.000Z","uid":60120,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"65d865ed7118e3905266e8a0333de5c366f412a4","tid":1721002,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbNXTWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbNXTWF.jpg&h=b5b65422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xrVZnP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxrVZnP0.jpg&h=27c68ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFloor plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/KHwNwJn.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHwNwJn.jpg&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=482ef3b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/KHwNwJn.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\nCCTV02<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sj4XOnghQSs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dsj4XOnghQSs&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=ee97ed56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sj4XOnghQSs</a><br />\nCCTV03<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WvMrZKEwX5A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWvMrZKEwX5A&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3ec1e9a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WvMrZKEwX5A</a><br />\nCCTV04<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tde8fL57a7Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTde8fL57a7Q&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=89eb6a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tde8fL57a7Q</a><br />\nCCTV05<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p3wVP2jdxRk&amp;t=38s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp3wVP2jdxRk%26t%3D38s&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=53d3bf06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p3wVP2jdxRk&amp;t=38s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有待各位判斷既供詞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tankBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tankBH.png&h=17975bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n//<br />\n另一名目擊者指，她當時駕車途經事發現場，目睹該男子從高處墮下，當場折斷雙手並失去知覺。// <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F...&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=af5ed902\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F...&h=bbc6d9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/...</a> //最早目擊者時間為2233<br />\n被發現係葵福路 嘉里物流外<br />\n無心跳 做緊cpr 同aed <br />\n手有復習性骨折<br />\n已上白車<br />\n白車車牌 a137<br />\n<br />\nFA 指無目擊者<br />\n但佢有急救牌 <br />\n睇骨折程度 似高處跌下 更似被斬 😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡<br />\n血債血償dklm <br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n結論：22:27~22:33為空白冇證據時段<br />\nCCTV唔似有做手腳<br />\n死者走入去就係為咗跳樓，好難解釋<br />\n動機依然可疑<br />\n如果係非自殺既話<br />\n唔排除有人call佢上去然後埋伏佢推佢落街<br />\n關鍵6分鐘既空白，證明唔到死者墮樓前附近冇人<br />\n<br />\n願逝者安息"},{"pid":"ffe106412d877eded9fa87ccb58cc14faf312c93","tid":1721002,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7fce9d85ddccf844af751327fcfb4190850ed07c","tid":1721002,"uid":75575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"你整合真係好齊好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br /