-14T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6141d5c8e60a524b50d525d1545b60b0c083ca0","tid":1721002,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c46b93b708023560047405546e14113f672e0392","tid":1721002,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4ed25ef717746734086946bba05af76ddc706c1","tid":1721002,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:13:09.000Z","msg":"9成9又炒車架啦，我覺得真係自殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"我只會睇證據<br />\nCCTV又冇去到22:33<br />\n唔會排除所有可能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"司徒敬在The Queen v Kwong Wing On &amp; another HCMA 574/1996案指出：「<ins>若用顯微鏡來細閱審訊謄本，便不難會發現有分歧出現、或證人無回答某問題、或部分地方存有固有不可能性、或證人給予警方的書面供詞有遺漏，及其他林林總總的點滴，作為支持上訴的理由。但在現實環境，即使誠實的證人亦會有證言前後不符及有遺漏的情況出現。反過來說，若沒有上述情況，則證人的證言便被批評是人工湊合而成的。上訴庭不會要求裁判官必須逐點處理辯方提出的各項細節，亦鼓勵裁判官以務實態度處理證據。當上訴一方以上述理由抨擊裁判官的裁斷時，上訴法庭須考慮的是，是否有實質及嚴重的偏差、遺漏或不合情理之處而令致法庭質疑案中事實重點的可信性。</ins>」"},{"pid":"157ccfb3cee550d04abe57337556ef6d9cbccb59","tid":1721002,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7887173400600013bbad7fad833e7af63e32741e","tid":1721002,"uid":246486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"682a80f186f35fefc4a95d29762a8eb9463afd73","tid":1721002,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:41:06.000Z","msg":"有埋平面圖解釋位置 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=